Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.67,0:01:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're holding a meeting of the Union Lords,\Nso we've been summoned to Jalucia.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.51,0:01:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Over six months since the Great Hall Tragedy,\Nand now there's finally a meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not exactly thrilled to go,\Nbut I suppose there's no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.27,0:01:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since that incident, everyone has had\Na keen interest in your next move.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.44,0:01:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps it's because you aided Sir Theo\Nin the battle for Savis.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.61,0:02:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Villar has certainly earned\Nhigh praise, in my opinion
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.79,0:02:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.91,0:02:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Alexis, who has since become\Nthe leader of the Union,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.79,0:02:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,does not wish to engage the Alliance in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.04,0:02:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,when was your birthday again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.72,0:02:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing. I can't believe you can\Nmanipulate multiple targets at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.98,0:02:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Once you get the hang of it, it's quite easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.44,0:02:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please show me how! I'd love to learn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I suppose I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.37,0:02:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.63,0:02:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.97,0:03:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd forgotten that Margaret's\N25th birthday was coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.22,0:03:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I may say so,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm well aware that you're always thinking\Nof our futures, and truly appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.44,0:03:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That said, Lady Margaret would prefer\Nto continue being under contract to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's a welcome thought, if true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.32,0:03:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, it wouldn't do to show\Nonly Margaret preferential treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.04,0:03:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Siluca.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.59,0:03:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to start making preparations\Nfor Margaret's birthday banquet right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.46,0:03:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Also, regarding the upcoming\NLords' meeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.38,0:03:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you,\NTheo and Lassic to accompany me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You wish to take Sir Theo as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.39,0:03:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Federico Rossini, the Viscount of Systina,\Nwill also be attending.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.31,0:03:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't hurt for Theo to meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.56,0:03:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for taking it into consideration.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.57,0:03:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No need to thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.40,0:04:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want you there to insist that\Nyou were the ones who started that battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And that I merely lent you a helping hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course we will, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Margaret, Happy Birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.43,0:04:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for looking after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be returning to\Nyour homeland after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.65,0:04:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all so glamorous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.53,0:04:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There will be dancing afterwards, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.99,0:04:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a skilled dancer, Sir Theo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not by a long shot!\NI've never even seen anyone dancing before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.91,0:04:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meletes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.33,0:04:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Margaret...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.83,0:04:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to wish you... a happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.59,0:05:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the long face, Siluca?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.72,0:05:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had hoped to learn\Nso much more from you, Lady Margaret.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Me, teach you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm Hellfire Margaret.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have nothing to teach but\Nbasic chemical spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I still have so much to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Siluca...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.24,0:05:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You might not be a mage\Nunder contract to Lord Villar,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.11,0:05:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but you've caused him trouble,\Nas well as received his favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.24,0:05:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.25,0:05:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you to take care\Nof Artuk and Lord Villar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone can see\Nthat they're made for each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.87,0:07:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But as outsiders, this is one thing\Nwe have no way of fixing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.59,0:07:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After seeing that amazing dance,\Nno time like the present!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One... Two... Three...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Try to keep to this rhythm,\Nand move your feet in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.91,0:08:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Move your body... a little closer to mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.95,0:08:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.08,0:08:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you do when you dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}T-Too close!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}R-Right in my face!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It looked a lot easier when I watched it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.52,0:08:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it was your first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was quite entertaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your talent lies more in buffoonery\Nthan in being a Lord, wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's as a buffoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.86,0:08:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to earn any praise from you, Lord Milza,\Nwould be a lifelong source of pride for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.03,0:08:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My dislike of you is confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.46,0:09:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't think you'd bring a shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free to make the first move!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.43,0:09:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd cross swords with you,\Nbut who knew you'd only defend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.82,0:09:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought this is how I should fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is not how a Lord should fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.04,0:09:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can only protect yourself behind a shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By eliminating your opponents,\Nyour allies will survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll save more allies in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.09,0:09:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And that is how...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.47,0:09:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,a Lord worthy of his title should fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.74,0:10:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you... for your instruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.25,0:10:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All other Lords are just like you,\Nhence why the era of Chaos drags on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.63,0:10:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Only one person can acquire\Nthe Emperor's Crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So why not determine the victor in battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.55,0:10:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Men like you, who lack ambition\Nand the mettle to protect your allies,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.22,0:10:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,have no right to be Lords.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.76,0:10:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I have a path I've sworn to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,An untold number of citizens have\Nlost their lives with you at the helm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.27,0:10:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And there will be many more in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That might be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:10:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you strive for oppression, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.58,0:11:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, I will serve as the fangs\Nof the one who becomes emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.75,0:11:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And my hope is that Lord Villar\Nwill turn out to be that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.43,0:11:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was a nervous wreck the entire time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You and me both.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.48,0:11:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever that man goes,\Na pile of enemy corpses will be in his wake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.19,0:11:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it's possible I could leave\Na trail of dead allies in mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.82,0:11:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it means to strive for justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Though I'd rather not go down such a path.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Theo, you have empathy for others,\Nand the power to fuse their souls into one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.58,0:11:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the path you seek to follow,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.59,0:11:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,was born from a desire you share with those\Nwho suffer under the Chaos and oppression.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.84,0:12:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning it's not just my path to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll go down that path with me, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.24,0:12:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much for the splendid party.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.86,0:12:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I may speak my mind,\NI wish I could've served you longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.74,0:12:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me happy to hear you say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But as you're a priestess of\Nthe order that worships the Sacred Flame,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.50,0:12:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,if I kept you here any longer,\NI'd get an earful from Dartania's viceroy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.01,0:12:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To tell the truth, I would've liked to\Nlean on your wisdom a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.84,0:12:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're basically the only one I can consult on foreign policy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...I find myself imposing on you in spite of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.14,0:12:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.27,0:12:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Regarding military and foreign policy matters,\NI think you'll be able to rely on Siluca.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.15,0:13:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The next Mage Leader, Laura,\Nis capable of handling domestic affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.03,0:13:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Siluca, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.87,0:13:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why she had\Nsuch an aversion to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.71,0:13:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She ate up all the "Lustful Earl"\Nrumors swirling around Eramu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In my mind, there's no man alive\Nwho treasures women more than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.09,0:13:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I find it hard to agree with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.47,0:13:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't think I treasure you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.35,0:13:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or is it that you just refuse\Nto get seriously involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.27,0:13:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.02,0:13:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Floria.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.11,0:13:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Daughter of the man who founded the Alliance,\Nthe Blood-and-Iron Earl, Jurgen Kreische.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.61,0:13:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.74,0:13:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She married into the Constance family,\Na member of the Alliance at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.96,0:13:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, my father, Lucien,\Ndefected to the Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:14:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Denied permission to return\Nto the Kreische clan,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and filled with a fierce hatred of my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My incarcerated mother began to abuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My mother couldn't forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.89,0:14:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"You have the corrupt\NConstance blood in your veins."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.36,0:14:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"You are not my child," she would tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.32,0:14:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.99,0:14:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's my earliest memory of my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.29,0:14:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I came to hate my mother,\Nand cursed my Kreische blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.33,0:14:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I revered my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So why do you now\Nfeel such reverence for Lady Floria?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.38,0:14:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as complicated as you'd think.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.34,0:14:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My mother was sure that father would fear\Nthe Kreische blood running in my veins.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:14:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was told that I resembled her, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.64,0:14:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:15:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Floria deliberately rejected you\Nso you wouldn't come to harm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.27,0:15:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But rather than despise the woman\Nwho gave birth to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.57,0:15:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...who wouldn't prefer to love her instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Villar...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please, do not cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.96,0:15:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I don't wish to talk on this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.67,0:15:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have always loved you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.80,0:15:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were the woman I could trust\Nmore than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.01,0:15:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, even though I worship women,\NI may also fear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.43,0:15:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And the reason I could never take you\Nas my bride was obvious from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All I hoped for was to remain\Nby your side, nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.45,0:15:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be praying that you find happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.21,0:16:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A meeting of the Lords will be held in Jalucia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Needless to say,\Nwe will have to attend as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, we'd travel by ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.43,0:16:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but this time, at the suggestion of\Na mage who dislikes the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.51,0:16:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we'll be making the trip together by land.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.64,0:16:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I shall invite you all\Nto my seaside castle another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Siluca, kindly go over the plan one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.11,0:16:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.99,0:16:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Due to Lord Lassic's conquest of Sievis,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.91,0:16:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the Lords of the neighboring Forbes and Clovis\Nare now immensely agitated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We will vanquish these two countries
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,as we make our way towards\Nthe Union nation of Ismeia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.13,0:16:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll send our troops back upon arrival,\Nwhile the rest of you will head on to Jalucia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Lassic, you will go to Forbes with Sir Theo,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.72,0:16:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,while the main unit will advance into Clovis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.26,0:16:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:17:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll deal with Lords who declare their intent\Nto remain with the Alliance in battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.23,0:17:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and send those who wish\Nto join the Union to the main unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is shaping up to be an epic stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go to the Lords' meeting,\Nbearing Forbes and Clovis as souvenirs!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.31,0:17:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have come to align ourselves\Nwith the Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.85,0:17:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Jericho Orlick, King of Forbes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.85,0:17:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He has resolved to remain with the Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's a bold resolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.23,0:17:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are the other Lords up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the northeast, Baron Brannis,\Na lLrd in service to the King of Forbes,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.28,0:17:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,has barricaded himself in a robust castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.24,0:18:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brannis, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.87,0:18:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hear they call him\Nthe Venomous Snake of Forbes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The free Lord Baron Ladvan\Nhas decided to side with the King of Forbes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.71,0:18:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Lassic?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.88,0:18:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I inquire if you would allow Sir Theo\Nto take care of Baron Ladvan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.56,0:18:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine by me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.02,0:18:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I shall seize the castle of this\Nso-called Venomous Snake of Forbes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.69,0:18:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wish me to lend you some troops?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.28,0:18:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can manage on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.91,0:18:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hand over your Crests to me,\Nand depart this territory without delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You may take any fortune you can carry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.63,0:18:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, you have\Nbut three days to withdraw.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.38,0:18:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you remain after that deadline,\NI cannot guarantee your survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.22,0:19:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.43,0:19:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How impetuous you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we discuss this in a more amicable way?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.10,0:19:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like over drinks at a banquet, Union-style.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.23,0:19:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I assure that my daughters will\Nshow you the utmost hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.86,0:19:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dartania is not a member of the Union.\NI request your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,True, if you're not inclined to negotiate,\Ntalking would just be a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.62,0:19:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is your intention?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That goes without saying. I will murder you,\Nand take over your Crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.63,0:19:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Brannis!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.00,0:19:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would treating an emissary this way\Nviolate the Lords' code?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.72,0:19:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You, there... What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.76,0:19:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Nikola.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Nikola, I want you to witness\Nwhat is about to transpire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.02,0:19:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing significant will occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.27,0:19:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing but the demise\Nof one misguided Lord, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd just handed over your Crest,\Nyou wouldn't need to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.54,0:20:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait–
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To kill a venomous snake, all you need to do\Nis stab the mouth it opens to bite you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.97,0:20:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-All at once–
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.29,0:20:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When it's just you against a horde,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.42,0:20:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it's easier to fight if they surround you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.63,0:20:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since everyone around you is your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.51,0:21:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,U-Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.58,0:21:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see to the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.41,0:21:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.17,0:21:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sooner or later, the Sievis forces\Nwill arrive to claim this castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.46,0:21:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be the one to relay how this came to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.88,0:21:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will gladly do as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.73,0:21:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, I've sacked this castle all by myself...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.19,0:21:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What will you do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.98,0:22:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MARCHING
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.99,0:23:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EPISODE 7:\NTHE WHITE PRINCE
